                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Paris, lorsque vient la froidure,\nAime, pendant la saison dure,\nA s'orner de martre et de vair.\nDésireux d'embellir ses fêtes\nPar toutes ces toisons de bêtes,\nIl a dit au bonhomme Hiver :"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "O vieil Hiver, père des glaces !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Qu'il neige sur mes larges places",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Et sous mes horizons étroits,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Comme là-bas, dans la Norvège,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Pour que je voie un peu de neige",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "En mil huit cent quatre-vingt-trois !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "O vieil Hiver, père des glaces !\nQu'il neige sur mes larges places\nEt sous mes horizons étroits,\nComme là-bas, dans la Norvège,\nPour que je voie un peu de neige\nEn mil huit cent quatre-vingt-trois !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Oh ! que la neige, de son lustre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Blanchisse mon bitume illustre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Pour que, poëte essentiel,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Je compare, en mes épigrammes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "La neige et les lys de mes femmes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Avec les lys tombés du ciel !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Oh ! que la neige, de son lustre,\nBlanchisse mon bitume illustre,\nPour que, poëte essentiel,\nJe compare, en mes épigrammes,\nLa neige et les lys de mes femmes\nAvec les lys tombés du ciel !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Tel, rêvant que sa face usée",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Fût blanche comme une épousée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Paris, en son désir goulu,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Demandait que la neige pure",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "L'enveloppât de sa guipure.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Le vieil Hiver n'a pas voulu.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tel, rêvant que sa face usée\nFût blanche comme une épousée,\nParis, en son désir goulu,\nDemandait que la neige pure\nL'enveloppât de sa guipure.\nLe vieil Hiver n'a pas voulu."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Il a dit : O ville de Flore,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Qui toujours vois tes lys éclore",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Et tes diamants refleurir ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Ville folle, heureuse, adulée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Pour toi la neige immaculée ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Allons, tu t'en ferais mourir !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Il a dit : O ville de Flore,\nQui toujours vois tes lys éclore\nEt tes diamants refleurir ;\nVille folle, heureuse, adulée,\nPour toi la neige immaculée ?\nAllons, tu t'en ferais mourir !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Quoi ! tes histrions et tes grues",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Sous leurs semelles incongrues",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Fouleraient la neige au flanc pur,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "La neige, divine pucelle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Dont l'âpre candeur étincelle",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Sous les caresses de l'azur !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Quoi ! tes histrions et tes grues\nSous leurs semelles incongrues\nFouleraient la neige au flanc pur,\nLa neige, divine pucelle,\nDont l'âpre candeur étincelle\nSous les caresses de l'azur !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Non. La neige avec orgueil touche",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Les champs nus où l'été farouche",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Faisait ruisseler des épis",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Qui sont la joie et la richesse.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Mais toi, courtisane et duchesse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Marche sur les riches tapis.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Non. La neige avec orgueil touche\nLes champs nus où l'été farouche\nFaisait ruisseler des épis\nQui sont la joie et la richesse.\nMais toi, courtisane et duchesse,\nMarche sur les riches tapis."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "La neige est faite pour les cimes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Où nous, les Dieux, nous nous assîmes ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Pour les monts, où la Vérité",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "N'entend pas de sourdes huées,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Et voit déchirer les nuées",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Par le vol de l'aigle irrité.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "La neige est faite pour les cimes\nOù nous, les Dieux, nous nous assîmes ;\nPour les monts, où la Vérité\nN'entend pas de sourdes huées,\nEt voit déchirer les nuées\nPar le vol de l'aigle irrité."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Toi, promène-toi dans la boue ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Et, plus tard, quand le soleil joue,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Dans tes bois aux sentiers fleuris.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Mais quant à la neige divine,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Je la garde pour la ravine.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Tu t'en ferais mourir, Paris.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Toi, promène-toi dans la boue ;\nEt, plus tard, quand le soleil joue,\nDans tes bois aux sentiers fleuris.\nMais quant à la neige divine,\nJe la garde pour la ravine.\nTu t'en ferais mourir, Paris."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Laisse au chamois la neige blanche.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Mais toi, peureux de l'avalanche,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Au son du luth et du hautbois",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "Dont la molle chanson t'effleure,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Foule, suivant le jour et l'heure,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "Ta pourpre, ou ton pavé de bois !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Laisse au chamois la neige blanche.\nMais toi, peureux de l'avalanche,\nAu son du luth et du hautbois\nDont la molle chanson t'effleure,\nFoule, suivant le jour et l'heure,\nTa pourpre, ou ton pavé de bois !"
        }
